{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be sleek and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0a2342;\n            --secondary-color: #243b55;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --highlight-color: #4ca5d0;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1.5rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--highlight-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: auto;\n            padding: 0 2rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            min-height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--highlight-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            max-width: 700px;\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            color: var(--highlight-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--highlight-color);\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 4rem 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--highlight-color);\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 2rem);\n            padding: 1rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--highlight-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 1rem 2rem;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #3a90b8;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Font Awesome for icons */\n        @import url('https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css');\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</h1>\n        <p>Your Trusted Partner in Digital Defense</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#hero\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Fortifying Your Digital Frontier</h2>\n            <p>We provide cutting-edge cybersecurity solutions to protect your business from evolving threats. From threat detection to incident response, we've got you covered.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h3>Risk Assessment</h3>\n                    <p>Identify vulnerabilities and understand your security posture.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-laptop-code\"></i>\n                    <h3>Penetration Testing</h3>\n                    <p>Simulate real-world attacks to uncover weaknesses.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-user-secret\"></i>\n                    <h3>Threat Intelligence</h3>\n                    <p>Stay ahead of emerging threats with proactive insights.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-bug\"></i>\n                    <h3>Incident Response</h3>\n                    <p>Swift and effective handling of security breaches.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i>\n                    <h3>Managed Security</h3>\n                    <p>24/7 monitoring and management of your security infrastructure.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i>\n                    <h3>Security Awareness Training</h3>\n                    <p>Empower your employees to be your first line of defense.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>SecureGuard Cybersecurity is dedicated to providing robust and reliable cybersecurity solutions. Our team of experts leverages the latest technologies and methodologies to ensure the safety and integrity of your digital assets. We believe in a proactive approach to security, helping you prevent breaches before they happen.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 SecureGuard Cybersecurity. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}